{"type":"question","id":24561,"title":"法轮功走入了哪些国家的校园？","uid":40857,"topics":[232,425],"contents":"<b>0.综述</b><br>\n<b>五大洲22国 法轮功走进海外校园</b><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/giOcTd8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/giOcTd8.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/giOcTd8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n2016年12月10日，法轮功学员到印度尼西亚巴淡岛国立七巴淡高中，教数百名学生炼法轮功<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhengjian.org/node/244881\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhengjian.org/node/244881</a><br>\n<br>\n<b>1.印度</b><br>\n法轮功经文列入印度一学校教材（图）<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.minghui.org/mh/articles/2008/10/6/187165.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.minghui.org/mh/articles/2008/10/6/187165.html</a><br>\n<a href=\"http://www.minghui.org/mh/articles/2008/10/6/187165.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/X2RC3z5.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/X2RC3z5.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/X2RC3z5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/licTTcE.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/licTTcE.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/licTTcE.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>2.意大利</b><br>\n法轮功走入意大利小学校园<br>\n<a href=\"https://blog.boxun.com/hero/201305/runwuxiwusheng66/37_1.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.boxun.com/hero/201305/runwuxiwusheng66/37_1.shtml</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xrsySK9.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xrsySK9.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xrsySK9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<b>3.台湾</b><br>\n台湾中大教授：《转法轮》启发研究思路<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.minghui.org/mh/articles/untrusted fake 2049bbss/2020/3/8/%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E